{"tid":1574370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"河南習語錄代十誡 教友︰中共是魔鬼","createTime":"2019-09-16T11:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T11:39:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb6e3554fb8e360643ecfdb6f62e72f22b7dfd1","tid":1574370,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190916/20769029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F20769029&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=308c2fc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F20769029&h=4ddc9169\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190916/20769029</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n河南習語錄代十誡 教友︰中共是魔鬼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190916/large/1568562978_c6ac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190916%2Flarge%2F1568562978_c6ac.gif&h=cbb7a172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教堂內的十誡被拆下。<br />\n<br />\n長期關注中國人權問題的《寒冬》雜誌近日報道，內地有教堂被當局屢次要求將十誡換成習近平語錄，甚至威脅「不聽黨的話，教堂就要立即關門」。與此同時，中共亦大範圍頻查宗教出版物，私印購買或出售非官方出版物遭罰。<br />\n<br />\n河南洛陽市某縣一官辦三自教堂的信徒，屢次被政府要求將十誡換成習近平語錄，並遭到政府訓斥。6月末，信徒被統戰部人員訓話：「一切都得聽黨的話，黨你讓幹啥就幹啥，不聽黨的話，教堂就要立即關門。」一名拒絕透露身份的信徒透露，截至目前，該縣幾乎所有三自教堂內的十誡都已被習語錄替代。一位官辦基督教教堂的傳道人表示，共產黨不僅要消滅家庭教會，也在蠶食基督教教義，有計劃地摧毀三自教會。該名講道人分析三自教堂的處境說，「共產黨的最終目的就是想當神。這也是魔鬼歷來做的事。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n禁出版宗教刊物<br />\n<br />\n此外，北京亦正從印刷、郵寄、流通、網絡等多領域，全方位加強對宗教出版物的限制。最近，福建的一名講道人計劃印刷170份紀念冊分發給在各地的同工。但印刷廠告訴他，紀念冊裏面宗教信息太明顯，除非更改封面，去掉紀念冊裏的十字架和所有的聖經經文，否則不能印刷。<br />\n<br />\n意大利《寒冬》雜誌 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n台駐港處長懸空15月破紀錄<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\niPhone 11不用「XI」 網民︰怕開罪習"},{"pid":"6e69c45e31b03d126a9934b1bf3e966ecf590164","tid":1574370,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvsTHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvsTHEi.jpg&h=e8bfe3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n TG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=cc0f667d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://instagram.com/suck.withyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsuck.withyou&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbYPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=14849b15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/suck.withyou</a></span>"},{"pid":"a3abd466da659592c26cd30d528e3b830da321df","tid":1574370,"uid":214534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:30:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵基督<br />\n大紅龍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5c007b84b9d60a2516df980d2ab22b205667b81e","tid":1574370,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"文革2.0開始左"},{"pid":"d85cebb6a0960937e5c052b57b95396395021699","tid":1574370,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T11:31:54.000Z","msg":"我是習近平